data.meta_description: Henry Hans Herman Schubert went home to be with the Lord Sept. 19, 2005, at the age of 91 at the Bonell Good Samaritan Center, Greeley, Colo.  He was born March 22, 1914, on the family farm near Ramona. He was the son of Albert and Augusta Schubert, the sixth of nine children.  He was raised on the farm and took over...
